f%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.g20.org%2Fen%2Fmedia-resources%2Fpress-releases%2Fnov-22%2Funveiling-of-logo%2F%5C%22%3Elogo%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20G20%20presidency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thus%20setting%20off%20a%20series%20of%20events%20linked%20to%20the%20global%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20Modi%20spotlighted%20%E2%80%9CLiFE%20(Lifestyle%20for%20Environment)%2C%20with%20its%20associated%2C%20environmentally%20sustainable%20and%20responsible%20choices%2C%20both%20at%20the%20level%20of%20individual%20lifestyles%20as%20well%20as%20national%20development%2C%20leading%20to%20globally%20transformative%20actions%20resulting%20in%20a%20cleaner%2C%20greener%20and%20bluer%20future%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20key%20goal%20of%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20G20%20presidency%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%20this%20can%20only%20be%20achieved%20by%20%E2%80%9Cstriving%20for%20just%20and%20equitable%20growth%20for%20all%20in%20the%20world%2C%20as%20we%20navigate%20through%20these%20turbulent%20times%2C%20in%20a%20sustainable%2C%20holistic%2C%20responsible%2C%20and%20inclusive%20manner%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvoking%20the%20legacy%20of%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BMahatma%20Basaveshwara%2C%20Dayanand%20Saraswati%2C%20Ramakrishna%20Paramahamsa%2C%20Ishwar%20Chandra%20Vidyasagar%2C%20Mahatma%20Phule%2C%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Dr%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcivil20.net%2Fc20-india-2023%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%3ECivil20%20(C20)%20India%20process%20was%20projected%20as%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20official%20engagement%20groups%20of%20the%20G20%20that%20provides%20a%20platform%20for%20civil%20society%20organisations%20(CSO)%20around%20the%20world%20to%20voice%20people%E2%80%99s%20aspirations%20to%20the%20world%20leaders%20in%20G20.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20website%20states%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Crepresents%20a%20democratic%2C%20participatory%2C%20and%20harmonious%20way%20of%20working%20together%E2%80%9D.%20C20%E2%80%99s%20goal%20is%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfocus%20on%20solving%20the%20socio-economic%20matters%20which%20touch%20the%20daily%20lives%20of%20the%20people%2C%20which%20include%20education%2C%20health%2C%20environment%2C%20technology%20and%20%3Cem%3Esewa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sense%20of%20service)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20C20%20process%20conducted%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcivil20.net%2Fc20-india-2023%2Forganisation%2Fc20-india-chair%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20guidance%20of%20spiritual%20leader%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcivil20.net%2Fc20-india-2023%2Forganisation%2Fc20-india-chair%2F%5C%22%3EMata%20Amritanandamayi%20(Amma)%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20has%20been%20curated%20to%20project%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcivil20.net%2Fvideos%2Fc20-inaugural-session%2F%5C%22%3Emajoritarian%20view%20of%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20massive%20public%20resources%2C%20C20%20events%20involved%20only%20those%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20academics%20and%20media%20comfortable%20with%20the%20bigoted%20Hindutva%20vision%20of%20India%20that%20is%20ideologically%20core%20to%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20party.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20symbol%2C%20the%20lotus%2C%20is%20also%20etched%20into%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20G20%20logo%2C%20leaving%20little%20doubt%20of%20its%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fg20-narendra-modi-one-india%5C%22%3EBefore%20%E2%80%98One%20World%2C%20One%20Family%2C%20One%20Future%E2%80%99%2C%20There%20Needs%20to%20Be%20%E2%80%98One%20India%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20essential%2C%20therefore%2C%20for%20progressive%20and%20independent%20voluntary%20organisations%2C%20people%E2%80%99s%20movements%2C%20independent%20research%20initiatives%2C%20free%20academics%2C%20media%20etc.%20to%20articulate%20their%20concerns%20about%20how%20the%20G20%20process%20was%20being%20employed%20%E2%80%93%20to%20project%20a%20deliberately%20coloured%20version%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20polity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20important%20to%20highlight%20how%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20governing%20India%20and%20causing%20massive%20democratic%20deficits.%20Such%20voices%20would%20never%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20official%20G20%20or%20C20%20engagement%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwgonifis.net%2F2023%2F08%2F17%2Fdelhi-set-to-witness-we20-a-peoples-summit-on-g20%2F%5C%22%3EWe20%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Summit%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20organised%20between%20August%2018%20and%2020%2C%202023%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwgonifis.net%5C%22%3EWorking%20Group%20on%20IFIs%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20HKS%20Surjeet%20Bhavan%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20space%20for%20the%20peoples%20of%20the%20G20%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20who%20collectively%20represent%20around%2085%25%20of%20the%20global%20GDP%2C%20over%2075%25%20of%20global%20trade%20and%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%20%E2%80%93%20to%20fathom%20risks%20in%20securing%20an%20inclusive%20and%20stable%20future%20in%20a%20fractured%20world%20riddled%20with%20crises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Modi%20administration%2C%20We20%20offered%20an%20incredible%20opportunity%20to%20demonstrate%20to%20the%20world%20that%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20building%20an%20inclusive%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20when%20the%20We20%20proceedings%20were%20underway%2C%20a%20little%20before%20noon%20on%20August%2019%2C%20a%20massive%20battalion%20of%20the%20Delhi%20police%20swept%20in%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwe20-summit-g20-delhi-police-jairam-ramesh%5C%22%3Ecordoned%20off%20the%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20military-style%20operation.%20Thus%2C%20the%20police%20effectively%20%3Cem%3Eimprisoned%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20400%20delegates%20from%20across%20India%20who%20were%20inside%20Surjeet%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19130257%2Fsignal-2023-08-19-130134_003-1024x461.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19130257%2Fsignal-2023-08-19-130134_003-1024x461.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19130257%2Fsignal-2023-08-19-130134_003-300x135.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19130257%2Fsignal-2023-08-19-130134_003.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668688%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22378%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBarricades%20were%20placed%20by%20police%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20venue%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98We20%E2%80%99%20summit.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20participants%2C%20including%20elders%20and%20women%20from%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20who%20had%20travelled%20from%20very%20far%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20summit%20and%20ensure%20their%20voices%20were%20heard%20as%20well%2C%20were%20denied%20entry%20into%20the%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipants%20were%20literally%20forced%20to%20stand%20by%20the%20cordoned%20gates%20and%20request%20the%20police%20to%20allow%20water%20and%20food%20to%20be%20passed%20through.%20Those%20outside%20were%20forced%20to%20stay%20on%20footpaths%20in%20the%20humid%20Delhi%20weather%20and%20under%20a%20scorching%20sun%2C%20without%20access%20to%20restrooms%20too.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20summit%20was%20being%20organised%20without%20their%20permission!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20police%20action%2C%20the%20session%20that%20was%20underway%20was%20titled%3A%20%E2%80%98Does%20the%20Modi%20Administration%20Really%20Deliver%20on%20Tackling%20Climate%20Change%2C%20to%20Protect%20the%20Environment%2C%20Biodiversity%20and%20Associated%20Human%20Rights%2C%20as%20Claimed%20With%20G20%20and%20Other%20Global%20Fora%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipating%20in%20this%20discussion%20were%20India%E2%80%99s%20former%20environment%20minister%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20Medha%20Patkar%20of%20the%20Narmada%20Bachao%20Andolan%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Anil%20Hegde%2C%20Vandana%20Shiva%20of%20Navdanya%20and%20the%20authors%20of%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20packed%20hall%20was%20engaged%20in%20deep%20conversations%20with%20the%20panel%20on%20how%20the%20Modi%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Finterview-why-there-is-mistrust-about-proposed-changes-to-forest-conservation-law%5C%22%3Eemasculated%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbiological-diversity-amendment-bill-passed-in-rajya-sabha-by-voice-vote%5C%22%3EBiological%20Diversity%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20and%20that%20this%20fundamentally%20weakened%20global%20action%20to%20effectively%20tackle%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomeone%20popped%20in%20to%20whisper%20the%20event%20was%20being%20forced%20shut%20by%20the%20police.%20Unfazed%2C%20the%20meeting%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1692805395600023561%5C%22%3EJairam%20Ramesh%20tweeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20later%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20extraordinary%20that%20Delhi%20Police%20is%20stopping%20people%20from%20attending%20the%20We20%20meeting%20organised%20by%20activists%20representing%20We%2C%20The%20People%2C%20inside%20a%20building%20that%20belongs%20to%20the%20CPM.%20The%20meeting%20is%20perfectly%20peaceful.%20There%20are%20no%20street%20protests.%20I%20managed%20to%20enter%20at%2010%3A30%20am%20before%20Delhi%20Police%20started%20its%20operations%20but%20had%20difficulty%20exiting%20now.%20This%20is%20New%20India%20Democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19173055%2FScreenshot-2023-08-19-at-5.28.39-1024x507.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19173055%2FScreenshot-2023-08-19-at-5.28.39-1024x507.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19173055%2FScreenshot-2023-08-19-at-5.28.39-300x149.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19173055%2FScreenshot-2023-08-19-at-5.28.39.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668742%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22416%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolice%20and%20security%20forces%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20venue%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98We20%E2%80%99%20summit.%20Photo%3A%20Debojit%20Dutta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter-of-fact%20reference%20to%20%E2%80%9CNew%20India%20Democracy%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20phrase%20Modi%20employs%20repeatedly%2C%20has%20frightening%20underpinnings.%20The%20Delhi%20police%20subsequently%20ensured%20that%20the%20We20%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Summit%20did%20not%20proceed%20on%20Sunday%2C%20August%2020%2C%20with%20a%20letter%20issued%20by%20the%20Central%20District%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20police%20(DCP)%20stating%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CRequest%20to%20hold%20meeting%20inside%20the%20premises%20and%20hall%20of%20HKS%20Surjeet%20Bhawan%20as%20part%20of%20G-20%20Summit%20by%20Working%20Group%20on%20IFIs%20on%2019%20%26amp%3B%2020.08.2023%20till%201800%20hours%20has%20been%20considered%20but%20due%20to%20law%20%26amp%3B%20order%2Ftraffic%20reason%2C%20and%20non-availability%20of%20the%20vital%20information%20pertaining%20to%20the%20gathering%2C%20visitors%2C%20etc.%20which%20is%20needed%20as%20per%20oreder%20%5Bsic%5D%20of%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20High%20Court%20of%20Delhi%20in%20W.P.(C)-2965%2F2023%2C%20dated%2010.03.2023%20above%20mentioned%20program%20is%20hereby%20rejected%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20review%20of%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20citation%20reveals%20it%20was%20specific%20to%20one%20event%20held%20in%20March%202023%2C%20and%20has%20no%20cross-cutting%20implications%20whatsoever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20conducted%20a%20search%20of%20the%20Delhi%20police%20website%20with%20the%20keywords%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20meeting%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cprior%20permission%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CG20%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20reveals%20no%20orders%20or%20circulars%20have%20been%20issued%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%20restricting%20the%20holding%20of%20such%20meetings%20or%20conventions%20or%20any%20other%20such%20events%20inside%20closed%20premises%2C%20anywhere%20in%20Delhi%20or%20in%20the%20sensitive%20central%20Delhi%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20review%20of%20the%20notifications%20issued%20(there%20are%20867%20records)%20reveals%20that%20on%20July%2012%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Central%20DCP%20issued%20one%20relating%20to%20ensuring%20public%20safety%20during%20the%20prevailing%20floods%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20another%20one%20on%20December%209%2C%202022%20inviting%20the%20public%20to%20reclaim%20recovered%20stolen%20articles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20written%20circular%20or%20order%20or%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%20in%202022%20or%202023%20empowers%20the%20Central%20District%20DCP%20to%20declare%2C%20even%20if%20under%20duress%20%E2%80%93%20as%20is%20apparent%20from%20his%20letter%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20We20%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Summit%20was%20being%20held%20illegally%20and%20can%20be%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20were%20to%20examine%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20summit%20created%20law%20and%20order%20and%20traffic%20problems%2C%20anyone%20visiting%20the%20venue%20would%20notice%20that%20it%20was%20held%20in%20an%20orderly%20and%20absolutely%20peaceful%20manner%2C%20within%20Surjeet%20Bhavan.%20And%20barring%20a%20few%20parked%20rickshaws%2C%20taxis%20and%20cars%2C%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20traffic%20anywhere%20in%20a%20kilometre%E2%80%99s%20radius%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20was%20during%20the%20week%E2%80%99s%20working%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20why%20the%20Delhi%20police%20imagined%20it%20was%20essential%20for%20them%20to%20collect%20%E2%80%9Cvital%20information%20pertaining%20to%20the%20gathering%2C%20visitors%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%20begs%20the%20question%3A%20will%20they%2C%20on%20such%20a%20premise%2C%20shut%20down%20trains%2C%20metros%20and%20bus%20stations%2C%20hotels%2C%20marriage%20gatherings%2C%20corporate%20get-togethers%2C%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20hospitals%2C%20public%20offices%2C%20etc.%20because%20none%20of%20these%20institutions%20gathers%20such%20%E2%80%9Cvital%20information%E2%80%9D%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe20-activists-blockade-police-modi-g20%5C%22%3EWe20%20Activists%20Brave%20the%20Blockade%20by%20Police%20Trained%20for%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20G-20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unfortunate%20police%20officer%E2%80%99s%20roving%20expedition%20in%20presenting%20rationality%20for%20what%20is%20clearly%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20citizens%20of%20this%20country%20to%20gather%20and%20conduct%20any%20event%20peacefully%20is%20how%20police%20power%20is%20being%20employed%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20leaders%20of%20the%20G20%20gather%20in%20September%20in%20Delhi%2C%20they%20need%20to%20reflect%20on%20what%20they%20are%20doing%20to%20India%20and%20its%20liberal%20democratic%20traditions.%20They%20cannot%20shy%20away%20from%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20active%20efforts%20underway%20to%20quell%20open%2C%20free%20and%20critical%20discussions%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20G20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20from%20Britain%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20and%20North%20American%20nations%20who%20espouse%20liberal%20democratic%20values%20need%20to%20take%20cognisance%20of%20this%20repressive%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20India.%20It%20will%20not%20be%20an%20easy%20task%20when%20several%20of%20the%20G20%20leaders%20are%20noted%20as%20governing%20their%20countries%20in%20rather%20undemocratic%20and%20even%20ruthless%20ways%20by%20various%20independent%20global%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20We20%20process%2C%20conducted%20independently%20without%20any%20fear%20or%20favour%2C%20introspected%20and%20interrogated%20vital%20concerns%20towards%20making%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20context%20of%20extensive%20climate%20change-related%20disasters%20across%20the%20world%20and%20brought%20to%20focus%20how%20existential%20crises%20due%20to%20climate%20change%20are%20colliding%20with%20the%20chaos%20resulting%20from%20neo-liberal%20economic%20models%2C%20manifesting%20in%20multiple%20ways%20in%20a%20multipolar%20world%20that%20is%20suffering%20from%20violent%20clashes%20between%20nations%20and%20amongst%20peoples%20within%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summit%20delved%20deep%20into%20the%20six-agenda%20priorities%20for%20the%202023%20G20%20dialogue%2C%20such%20as%20green%20development%2C%20climate%20finance%20%26amp%3B%20LiFE%2C%20accelerated%2C%20inclusive%20and%20resilient%20growth%2C%20accelerating%20progress%20on%20sustainable%20development%20goals%2C%20technological%20transformation%20%26amp%3B%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20multilateral%20institutions%20for%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20and%20women-led%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coming%20together%20of%20peoples%2C%20movements%2C%20trade%20unions%2C%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20concerned%20individuals%20and%20affected%20communities%20to%20deliberate%20on%20such%20critical%20issues%20should%20have%20been%20welcomed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20could%20have%20issued%20a%20direction%20to%20all%20his%20cabinet%20colleagues%20and%20ensured%20there%20were%20ministry%20representatives%20attending%20and%20listening%20to%20what%20people%20from%20across%20India%20%E2%80%93%20most%20of%20who%20had%20come%20with%20their%20own%20resources%20%E2%80%93%20were%20saying.%20Was%20the%20Modi%20administration%20so%20scared%20of%20learning%20the%20truth%20that%20it%20instead%20chose%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20We20%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Summit%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELeo%20F.%20Saldanha%20and%20Bhargavi%20S.%20Rao%20are%20public%20policy%20analysts%20associated%20with%20Environment%20Support%20Group%2C%20an%20intersectional%2C%20intersectoral%20and%20interdisciplinary%20research%2C%20campaign%20and%20advocacy%20initiative%20based%20in%20Bangalore.%C2%A0%20They%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aleo%40esgindia.org%5C%22%3Eleo%40esgindia.org%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Abhargavi%40esgindia.org%5C%22%3Ebhargavi%40esgindia.org%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692626401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21122023%2FIMG_3083.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe20-summit-modi-truth-g20%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20present%20administration%2C%20We20%20offered%20an%20incredible%20opportunity%20to%20demonstrate%20to%20the%20world%20that%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20building%20an%20inclusive%20India.%22%2C%22author