aking%20at%20the%20launch%20of%20NDTV's%20Madhya%20Pradesh-Chhattisgarh%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'INDIA'%2C%20which%20stands%20for%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%2C%20is%20hoping%20to%20block%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20from%20coming%20to%20power%20again%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20welfare%20schemes%20announced%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BActions%20should%20speak%20louder%20than%20words.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20remembered%20sisters%20and%20farmers%2018%20years%20later.%20Why%20did%20they%20need%20to%20make%20these%20announcements%20five%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%3F%20He%20is%20trying%20to%20wash%20his%20sins%20of%20eighteen%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20from%202004%20to%202009%2C%20drew%20a%20parallel%20between%20the%20election%20guarantees%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20welfare%20measures%20announced%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20talked%20about%20relief%20to%20common%20people%2C%20we%20didn't%20have%20elections%20in%20our%20mind.%20We%20will%20be%20happy%20if%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20announces%20gas%20cylinder%20at%20Rs%20500.%20And%20I%20have%20heard%20he%20is%20going%20to%20make%20that%20announcement.%20After%20our%20announcements%2C%20he%20is%20thinking%20of%20cylinders%20and%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20said%20we%20would%20give%20Rs%201500%2C%20he%20said%20he%20would%20give%20Rs%202%2C000.%20If%20they%20do%20it%2C%20it%20fulfils%20our%20goal%20as%20our%20goal%20is%20not%20votes%2C%20but%20people's%20welfare%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiding%20high%20on%20its%20Karnataka%20win%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20announced%20%26quot%3Belection%20guarantees%26quot%3B%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20-%20similar%20to%20the%20ones%20it%20implemented%20in%20the%20southern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress'%20promise%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Gas%20cylinder%3A%20Rs%20500%3B%201%2C500%20per%20month%20to%20every%20woman%3B%20Electricity%3A%20100%20units%20waived%2C%20200%20units%20halved%3B%20farm%20loan%20waived%3B%20old%20pension%20scheme%20will%20be%20applicable.%20We%20kept%20our%20promise%20in%20Karnataka%20-%20now%20we%20will%20keep%20it%20in%20MP%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20had%20said%20in%20a%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20in%20power%20in%20the%20central%20state%20since%202003%2C%20except%20for%20a%20break%20between%20December%202018%20and%20March%202020%20when%20the%20state%20had%20a%20Congress%20government%20under%20Kamal%20Nath.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692625920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fkcdiane_kamal-nath-ndtv_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkamal-nath-on-what-will-make-india-bloc-stay-united-anybody-but-modi-4316105%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20will%20iron%20out%20their%20differences%20and%20stick%20together%20because%20their%20motto%20is%20%26quot%3Banybody%2C%20but%20Modi%26quot%3B%2C%20insisted%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20state%20chief%20Kamal%20Nath%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkamal-nath-on-what-will-make-india-bloc-stay-united-anybody-but-modi-4316105%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkamal-nath-on-what-will-make-india-bloc-stay-united-anybody-but-modi-4316105%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkamal-nath-on-what-will-make-india-bloc-stay-united-anybody-but-modi-4