-July%20with%20a%20starting%20price%20of%20CA%2450.%20Over%20the%20next%20month%2C%20more%20than%201%2C700%20bids%20poured%20in%20for%20the%20unusual%20outfit.%20It%20was%20eventually%20won%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fprimetimedonair%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E25-store%20Alberta%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%20PrimeTime%20Donair%20and%20Poutine%2C%20which%20made%20the%20winning%20bid%20of%20CA%2416%2C025.%20Other%20donair%20stores%2C%20including%20the%20King%20of%20Donair%2C%20Blowers%20%26amp%3B%20Grafton%2C%20and%20Swiss%20Donair%2C%20also%20placed%20bids%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsurplus.gov.ab.ca%2FOA%2FItemDetail.aspx%3FAuctionID%3D43311%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauction%20records%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20listing%20said%20the%20costume%20was%20made%20from%20various%20latexes%2C%20vulcanized%20rubbers%2C%20and%20synthetic%20materials%2C%20and%20had%20adjustable%20shoulder%20straps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComes%20with%20silver%20colored%20Body%20Suit%20for%20that%20authentic%20tinfoil%20look!%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20listing%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20outfit%20from%20head%20to%20toe%20is%20six%20foot%20three%20tall%2C%20while%20the%20donair%20body%20suit%20is%20four%20foot%20eight.%20The%20listing%20said%20the%20costume%20is%20in%20%26quot%3Bexcellent%26quot%3B%20visual%20condition%20but%20is%20%26quot%3Bdusty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20saw%20it%20in%20person%2C%20it%20blew%20me%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Adil%20Asim%20of%20Primetime%20Donair%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLuTZLKhE_MM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECTV%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanadian%20national%20broadcaster%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fedmonton%2Fdonair-costume-winner-alberta-1.6936780%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20costume%20was%20created%20by%20special-effects%20studio%20Alterian%20in%202015%20for%20a%20traffic-safety%20video%20about%20driving%20while%20high%20on%20cannabis%2C%20but%20that%20it%20was%20never%20worn%20after%20the%20campaign%20was%20canceled.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Alberta%20government%20said%20on%20the%20auction%20site%20that%20the%20costume%20%26quot%3Bwas%20a%20prop%20for%20an%20advertising%20campaign%20and%20is%20no%20longer%20required%20by%20the%20department.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20donair%20is%20a%20Canadian%20dish%20made%20of%20shavings%20of%20spiced%20ground%20beef%20that%20has%20been%20roasted%20on%20a%20vertical%20rotisserie.%20The%20beef%20is%20placed%20inside%20a%20thin%2C%20Lebanese-style%20pita%20alongside%20with%20tomato%2C%20raw%20onion%2C%20and%20%E2%80%93%20contentiously%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20lettuce%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20region.%20It's%20topped%20with%20a%20sauce%20made%20from%20evaporated%20milk%2C%20vinegar%2C%20garlic%2C%20and%20sugar%2C%20and%20is%20served%20wrapped%20in%20tinfoil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dish%20was%20developed%20by%20Peter%20Gamalakos%2C%20who%20opened%20Halifax's%20first%20donair%20shop%2C%20the%20King%20of%20Donair%2C%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20multiple%20sources%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodnetwork.ca%2Farticle%2Fthe-delicious-history-of-the-halifax-donair%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Food%20Network%2C%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20CBC%20reported%20that%20Gamoulakos%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20by%20tweaking%20the%20recipe%20for%20a%20Greek%20gyro%20after%20locals%20didn't%20like%20the%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20donair%20costume%20shows%20the%20inclusion%20of%20lettuce%20in%20the%20wrap%2C%20which%20sparked%20a%20bidding%20war%20between%20Edmonton%20and%20Halifax%20donair%20stores%2C%20with%20those%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%20saying%20they%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66505627%3F_hsmi%3D271025890%26_hsenc%3Dp2ANqtz-8qAcnGsOdhFZu0G2Lca_dkkk