hi%20Lieutenant-Governor%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-law%2Fgujarat-pasa-act-lg-has-approved-for-delhi-8834910%2F%5C%22%3Eapproved%20the%20use%20of%20a%20Gujarat%20preventive%20detention%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Delhi.%20This%20law%20grants%20the%20police%20the%20power%20to%20detain%20individuals%20for%20extended%20periods%20without%20trial%20and%20even%20before%20any%20actual%20offence%20is%20committed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20police%20have%20often%20displayed%20a%20blatant%20disregard%20for%20notions%20of%20fairness%2C%20impartiality%20and%20due%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20unabashedly%20pursued%20student%20activists%2C%20journalists%20and%20politicians%20opposed%20to%20the%20regime%2C%20creating%20an%20environment%20of%20fear%20and%20intimidation.%20This%20disturbing%20trend%20reached%20its%20peak%20with%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20false%20implications%20of%20student%20activists%20under%20the%20draconian%20anti-terror%20law%2C%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%2C%20and%20the%20law%20of%20sedition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20afraid%20that%20giving%20the%20Delhi%20police%20powers%20under%20the%20draconian%20Gujarat%20Prevention%20of%20Anti-Social%20Activities%20Act%2C%201985%20will%20further%20fuel%20unaccountability%20and%20arbitrariness%20in%20their%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventive%20detention%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20coercive%20tools%20that%20a%20state%20in%20a%20constitutional%20democracy%20has%20at%20its%20disposal.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20past%20has%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Crepugnant%20to%20democratic%20ideas%20and%20an%20anathema%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20law%20is%20inherently%20arbitrary%20and%20sweeping%20in%20scope%2C%20enabling%20its%20massive%20and%20flagrant%20abuse.%20The%20high%20court%20of%20Gujarat%20has%20repeatedly%20censured%20the%20executive%20for%20misusing%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%20it%E2%80%99s%20shocking%20that%20the%20consent%20to%20extend%20the%20Gujarat%20law%20in%20Delhi%20was%20given%20without%20any%20public%20consultation.%20Though%20the%20subject%20of%20policing%20is%20outside%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20elected%20Delhi%20government%2C%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20the%20elected%20government%20can%20be%20completely%20sidestepped%20on%20matters%20of%20law%20and%20order.%20On%20a%20matter%20as%20important%20as%20bringing%20into%20Delhi%20the%20preventive%20detention%20law%2C%20the%20LG%20should%20have%20consulted%20the%20chief%20minister.%20However%2C%20with%20an%20iron%20grip%2C%20the%20office%20of%20LG%20has%20arrogated%20despotic%20powers%2C%20effectively%20eclipsing%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20elected%20government%20in%20all%20important%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewspapers%20have%20reported%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20after%20the%20Delhi%20police%20wrote%20to%20the%20L-G%20asking%20for%20a%20stricter%20law%20to%20deal%20with%20snatchers%20and%20drug%20peddlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20a%20lame%20excuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHas%20the%20crime%20of%20chain%20snatching%20and%20drug%20peddling%20in%20Delhi%20reached%20such%20proportions%20that%20it%20warrants%20action%20under%20preventive%20detention%20law%20instead%20of%20the%20normal%20process%20of%20investigation%20followed%20by%20a%20criminal%20trial%3F%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20snatchers%20and%20drug%20peddlers%20be%20booked%20under%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20Narcotic%20Drugs%20and%20Psychotropic%20Substances%20Act%2C%201985%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20reliable%2C%20cogent%20data%20has%20been%20provided%20to%20justify%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20preventive%20detention%20law%20in%20Delhi.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20introduction%20of%20such%20a%20harsh%20and%20unfair%20law%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20shows%20how%20the%20Delhi%20LG%20operates%20in%20an%20authoritarian%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventive%20detention%20laws%20were%20justified%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20debates%20as%20an%20evil%20necessity.%20Article%20246%20read%20with%20Seventh%20Schedule%2C%20List%20I%2C%20Entry%203%2C%20empowers%20the%20Parliament%20to%20pass%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20for%20reasons%20connected%20with%20defence%2C%20foreign%20affairs%20or%20security%20of%20India%2C%20and%20by%20List%20III%2C%20Entry%209%2C%20empowers%20the%20Parliament%20and%20state%20legislatures%20to%20pass%20these%20laws%20for%20reasons%20connected%20with%20the%20security%20of%20a%20State%2C%20the%20maintenance%20of%20public%20order%2C%20or%20the%20maintenance%20of%20supplies%20and%20services%20essential%20to%20the%20community.%20Article%2022%20provides%20important%20procedural%20safeguards%20against%20arbitrary%20and%20procedurally%20irregular%20preventive%20detention%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarats-prevention-of-anti-social-activities-act-a-free-pass-for-arbitrary-detentions%5C%22%3EGujarat%E2%80%99s%20Preventive%20Detention%20Law%20Is%20a%20Free%20Pass%20For%20Police%20to%20Act%20Without%20Evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20intended%20for%20use%20in%20extraordinary%20situations%20threatening%20the%20security%20of%20the%20state%20or%20public%20order%2C%20the%20use%20of%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20has%20unfortunately%20become%20a%20routine%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Gujarat%20have%20enacted%20such%20laws%20as%20a%20convenient%20shortcut%20to%20bypass%20the%20normal%20process%20of%20laws%20and%20the%20rigours%20of%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system.%20The%20state%20laws%20are%20in%20addition%20to%20four%20central%20preventive%20detention%20laws%3A%C2%A0the%20Conservation%20of%20Foreign%20Exchange%20and%20Prevention%20of%20Smuggling%20Act%20(COFEPOSA)%2C%201972%3B%C2%A0the%20Prevention%20of%20Black%20Marketing%20and%20Maintenance%20of%20Supplies%20of%20Essential%20Commodities%20Act%2C%201980%3B%C2%A0the%20National%20Security%20Act%2C%201980%3B%C2%A0and%C2%A0the%20Prevention%20of%20Illicit%20Traffic%20in%20Narcotic%20Drugs%20and%20Psychotropic%20Substances%20Act%2C%201988.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20the%20existing%20central%20preventive%20detention%20laws%2C%20which%20focus%20on%20national%20and%20economic%20security%20matters%2C%20the%20state%20laws%20have%20transformed%20into%20catch-all%20measures%20that%20encompass%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20offences%20and%20situations%20unrelated%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20security%20or%20public%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202017%20onwards%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Fpreventive-detentions-in-2021-up-by-237-compared-to-year-before%2Farticle65853863.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DData%2520pertaining%2520to%25202021%2520showed%2Csix%2520months%2520of%2520their%2520detention.%5C%22%3Econsistent%20upward%20trend%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20number%20of%20individuals%20held%20in%20preventive%20custody.%20In%20the%20year%202021%20alone%2C%20the%20figure%20reached%20a%20staggering%201.1%20lakh%20people%2C%20showing%20an%20alarming%20surge%20of%20over%2023.7%25%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20those%20detained%20were%20facing%20charges%20related%20to%20smuggling%2C%20bootlegging%2C%20theft%2C%20gambling%2C%20robbery%20and%20sexual%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShockingly%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarats-prevention-of-anti-social-activities-act-a-free-pass-for-arbitrary-detentions%5C%22%3Ehas%20used%20the%20preventive%20detention%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20detain%20individuals%20accused%20of%20GST%20evasion%2C%20unauthorised%20sale%20of%20anti-Covid%20medicines%2C%20cow%20smuggling%2C%20and%20even%20cases%20involving%20interfaith%20couples.%20This%20troubling%20data%20reveals%20an%20ever-widening%20net%20of%20preventive%20detention%20being%20cast%20for%20matters%20that%20extend%20far%20beyond%20the%20realm%20of%20national%20security%20or%20public%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventive%20detention%20laws%20have%20become%20a%20convenient%20tool%20to%20bypass%20the%20rigorous%20procedures%20of%20criminal%20law.%20This%20includes%20evading%20the%20legal%20obligation%20to%20produce%20an%20accused%20before%20a%20magistrate%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20filing%20chargesheets%20within%2060%2F90%20days%2C%20presenting%20a%20compelling%20case%20for%20denial%20of%20bail%2C%20and%20ultimately%20proving%20guilt%20beyond%20reasonable%20doubt%20to%20secure%20a%20conviction.%20These%20crucial%20requirements%20of%20ordinary%20criminal%20law%20are%20willingly%20sacrificed%20in%20the%20name%20of%20maintaining%20public%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20state%20preventive%20detention%20laws%2C%20including%20the%20Gujarat%20law%2C%20are%20constitutionally%20suspect.%20They%20give%20arbitrary%20and%20unguided%20power%20to%20the%20executive%20without%20prescribing%20any%20guidelines%2C%20controls%20or%20checks%20for%20its%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20what%20point%20does%20the%20previous%20record%20of%20ordinary%20crimes%20transform%20an%20accused%20into%20a%20potential%20threat%20to%20public%20order%2C%20warranting%20their%20detention%20under%20preventive%20measures%3F%20Where%20does%20the%20threshold%20lie%20for%20offences%20such%20as%20video%20piracy%2C%20chain-snatching%2C%20bootlegging%2C%20or%20food%20adulteration%20to%20be%20perceived%20as%20jeopardising%20public%20order%3F%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20statutes%20fail%20to%20offer%20any%20guidance%20on%20these%20vital%20aspects%2C%20leaving%20the%20matter%20shrouded%20in%20ambiguity%20and%20subject%20to%20arbitrary%20interpretation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20established%20a%20comprehensive%20set%20of%20guidelines%20that%20must%20be%20adhered%20to%20by%20authorities%20when%20issuing%20preventive%20detention%20orders.%20However%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20be%20clear%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20at%20best%20a%20mere%20band-aid%2C%20applied%20to%20a%20deeply%20disturbing%20crisis%20threatening%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dangerous%20course%20of%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20is%20fuelling%20the%20descent%20into%20authoritarianism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20inadequate%20judicial%20scrutiny%20of%20state%20preventive%20detention%20laws.%20They%20have%20not%20been%20tested%20on%20the%20anvil%20of%20Articles%2014%2C%2019%20and%20Article%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20long%20ago%2C%20Justice%20Rohinton%20Nariman%20(now%20retired)%20presiding%20over%20a%20case%20of%20preventive%20detention%20under%20the%20Telangana%20statute%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjudicial-intervention-barely-deters-telangana-ap-govts-from-abusing-preventive-detention-laws%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20astonishment%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20constitutional%20challenge%20to%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20State%20law%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20like%20the%20Gujarat%20Anti-Social%20Activities%20Act%20have%20effectively%20become%20a%20backdoor%20through%20which%20the%20state%20executive%20can%20thwart%20bail%20orders%20obtained%20by%20the%20accused%20or%20keep%20individuals%20imprisoned%20without%20securing%20a%20conviction%20through%20a%20fair%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incarceration%20of%20nearly%20one%20lakh%20people%20every%20year%20under%20a%20panoply%20of%20different%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20is%20a%20grim%20reminder%20of%20the%20serious%20curtailment%20of%20constitutionally%20guaranteed%20freedoms%20and%20civil%20liberties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20also%20reveals%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20those%20detained%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Telangana%20under%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20hail%20from%20the%20poorest%20and%20most%20vulnerable%20sections%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20police%20have%20repeatedly%20and%20shockingly%20demonstrated%20a%20flagrant%20disregard%20for%20the%20fundamental%20principles%20of%20fairness%2C%20and%20due%20process.%20The%20absolute%20worst%20scenario%20for%20Delhi%20is%20to%20further%20empower%20its%20police%20with%20additional%20arbitrary%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAshish%20Khetan%20is%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20at%20Jindal%20Global%20Law%20School%2C%20Sonipat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692624652000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01195459%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-06-01-at-4.40.30-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-lgs-approval-to-use-gujarat-preventive-detention-law-raises-alarms-on-unchecked-state-power%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20police%20have%20often%20displayed%20a%20blatant%20disregard%20for%20notions%20of%20fairness%2C%20impartiality%20and%20due%20process.%20The%20absolute%20worst%20scenario%20for%20Delhi%20is%20to%20further%20empower%20its%20police%20with%20additional%20arbitrary%20powers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AAP%20to%20be%20part%20of%20next%20oppn%20meet%20despite%20uneasy%20Cong%20ties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692624591000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102913373%2Cimgsize-53094.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Farvind-kejriwal-india-mumbai-meeting-opposition-meeting-congress-chhattisgarh-delhi-congress-punjab-congress-aap-aam-aadmi-party%2Farticleshow%2F10291