%20Keep%20Running%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3F%20What%20Chief%20Minister%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20known%20to%20have%20a%20an%20amiable%20persona%20since%20he%20headed%20the%20state%20in%202005%2C%20has%20acquired%20a%20new%20image%20ahead%20of%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%20The%2064-year-old%2C%20seen%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BMama%20(maternal%20uncle)%26quot%3B%20has%20acquired%20the%20monicker%20%26quot%3BBulldozer%20Mama%26quot%3B%20after%20bulldozer%20action%20against%20a%20handful%20of%20people%20in%20the%20state.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20bulldozer%20action%20will%20continue%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%2C%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20as%20part%20of%20a%20special%20programme%20to%20launch%20NDTV's%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chhattisgarh%20channel%2C%20answered%20in%20the%20affirmative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20became%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20at%20the%20end%20of%202005.%20That%20time%2C%20there%20were%20three%20problems%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20first%20was%20the%20terror%20of%20dacoits%20in%20Chambal.%20I%20had%20said%20that%20either%20Shivraj%20will%20stay%20on%20the%20soil%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20or%20the%20dacoits.%20The%20two%20cannot%20coexist.%20I%20ended%20all%20dacoity%20within%20a%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chouhan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ended%20the%20Maoist%20activities...%20I'm%20as%20soft%20as%20flowers%20for%20the%20people.%20But%20if%20I%20am%20soft%20towards%20everybody%2C%20who%20will%20control%20dacoits%20and%20Maoists%2C%20mafia%2C%20or%20criminals%20who%20assault%20women%3F%20So%20the%20bulldozers%20will%20keep%20running.%20Why%20is%20it%20an%20issue%3F%20They%20are%20criminals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20has%20seen%20frequent%20bulldozer%20action%20over%20the%20last%20months%2C%20following%20the%20trend%20in%20BJP-ruled%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20July%2C%20the%20house%20of%20Pravesh%20Shukla%2C%20accused%20of%20urinating%20on%20a%20Dalit%20man%2C%20was%20razed%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20state%20government.%20The%20accused%20was%20arrested%20after%20the%20video%2C%20where%20he%20was%20seen%20urinating%20on%20a%20man%2C%20was%20widely%20circulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20month%2C%20the%20houses%20of%20two%20men%20accused%20of%20raping%20and%20brutalising%20a%2012-year-old%20girl%20in%20the%20temple%20town%20of%20Maihar%20in%20Satna%20district%20were%20razed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20razing%20of%2010%20houses%20belonging%20to%20people%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20in%20Raipura%20village%20of%20Sagar%20district%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row.%20Six%20of%20the%20houses%20were%20built%20under%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana.%20The%20Forest%20Department%20said%20only%20those%20who%20were%20illegally%20occupying%20the%20government%20forest%20land%20were%20evicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20huge%20criticism%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20the%20government%20suspended%20the%20ranger%20who%20ordered%20the%20demolition%20and%20said%20the%20houses%20will%20be%20reconstructed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692624060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Frcq3j8m8_shivraj-chouhan-ndtv-650_650x400_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-bulldozers-keep-running-in-madhya-pradesh-what-chief-minister-said-4316285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20known%20to%20have%20a%20an%20amiable%20persona%20since%20he%20headed%20the%20state%20in%202005%2C%20has%20acquired%20a%20new%20image%20ahead%20of%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22htt