ak%20O%20Gabeshak%20Sangha%20in%20December%202021.%20This%20organisation%20is%20the%20Bengal%20unit%20of%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAkhil%20Bharatiya%20Rashtriya%20Shaikshik%20Mahasangh%20(ABRSM)%2C%20which%20has%20links%20to%20both%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20Sau%20has%20also%20been%20an%20active%20member%20of%20the%20All%20Bengal%20University%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Association%20(ABUTA)%20JU%20chapter%2C%20known%20for%20its%20connections%20to%20SUCI%20and%20WEBCUPA%20%E2%80%93%20the%20teachers%E2%80%99%20wing%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tenure%20of%20JU%E2%80%99s%20last%20full-time%20vice-chancellor%20Suranjan%20Das%20ended%20on%20May%2031.%20Following%20that%2C%20the%20governor%20appointed%20Amitabha%20Datta%2C%20the%20pro-VC%20of%20the%20varsity%2C%20as%20the%20officiating%20vice-chancellor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Sau%20led%20a%20delegation%20of%20teachers%20to%20the%20governor%20and%20made%20an%20official%20complaint%20against%20Datta%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20latter%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3Erunning%20the%20campus%20through%20an%20ad-hoc%20mechanism.%20This%20led%20to%20Datta%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98s%20removal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20officiating%20VC%2C%20Sau%E2%80%99s%20past%20social%20media%20activity%20has%20attracted%20attention.%20On%20Facebook%2C%20he%20has%20shared%20a%20homophobic%20meme%2C%20while%20another%20presents%20a%20meme%20with%20questionable%20content%20regarding%20women.%20He%20has%20also%20expressed%20support%20for%20economic%20status%20as%20the%20criteria%20for%20reservations%2C%20not%20caste%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20agenda.%20Sau%20has%20also%20shared%20a%20post%20endorsing%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21184652%2Fsau-social-media.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21184652%2Fsau-social-media.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21184652%2Fsau-social-media-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21184652%2Fsau-social-media-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21184652%2Fsau-social-media-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669036%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EScreenshots%20of%20some%20posts%20that%20Buddadeb%20Sau%20has%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESau%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20outrage%20and%20scepticism.%20Critics%20point%20to%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20that%20stipulated%20that%20a%20VC%20must%20possess%20a%20minimum%20of%2010%20years%20of%20teaching%20experience%20as%20a%20professor%20in%20a%20university%2C%20which%20according%20to%20them%2C%20Sau%20falls%20short%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20appointment%20raises%20questions%20about%20his%20eligibility.%20The%20ongoing%20power%20struggle%20between%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20governor%20over%20the%20VC%20position%20is%20further%20undermining%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20educational%20institutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20commented%20Sujan%20Chakraborty%2C%20a%20CPI(M)%20leader%20and%20an%20alumnus%20of%20the%20University.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENalasis%20Basu%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20CPI%E2%80%99s%20student%20wing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAISA%2C%20said%20that%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20governor%20has%20%E2%80%9Ccapitalised%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20turmoil%20in%20the%20university%20to%20%E2%80%9Cindirectly%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20involvement%E2%80%9D%20through%20the%20new%20VC.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20manoeuvring%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20trend%20wherein%20individuals%20are%20strategically%20placed%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20educational%20institutions%20to%20undermine%20their%20integrity.%20This%20has%20been%20seen%20at%20institutions%20like%20Visva-Bharati.%20Now%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20Jadavpur%20University.%20By%20complying%20with%20directives%20from%20the%20central%20government%2C%20the%20Governor%20has%20placed%20an%20individual%20with%20insufficient%20professorial%20experience%20as%20VC%2C%E2%80%9D%20Basu%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20BJP-RSS%20continues%20their%20efforts%20to%20infiltrate%20Jadavpur%20University%20in%20this%20manner%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20anticipated%20that%20resistance%20from%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20students%20will%20grow%20stronger.%20Jadavpur%20University%20stands%20firm%20against%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20AISA%20leader%20remarked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20governor%20has%20made%20Jadavpur%20University%20a%20lab%20for%20his%20experiments.%20We%20would%20get%20to%20know%20the%20result%20soon.%20Those%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%20%5Bin%20connection%20with%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20death%5D%20are%20all%20left-wing%20activists.%20It%E2%80%99s%20clear%20who%20all%20were%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Trinankur%20Bhattacharya%2C%20state%20president%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20Chhatra%20Parishad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20making%20attempts%20to%20establish%20a%20foothold%20within%20the%20precincts%20of%20JU%2C%20where%20its%20sphere%20of%20influence%20has%20been%20limited.%20BJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20last%20week%20visited%20Jadavpur%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fju-students-death-suvendu-adhikaris-jadavpur-university-visit-turns-chaotic-as-clashes-break-out%2Fcid%2F1959664%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20BJP%20after%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ehaving%20%E2%80%9Ctaught%20a%20lesson%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98Tukde-tukde%E2%80%99%20gang%20in%20JNU%2C%20will%20%E2%80%9Ccleanse%E2%80%9D%20Jadavpur%20as%20well%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20%E2%80%9Ctukde-tukde%20gang%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20catch-all%20phrase%20that%20the%20BJP%20uses%20to%20refer%20to%20its%20critics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESFI%20leader%20Mayukh%20Biswas%20said%20that%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJadavpur%20University%20is%20among%20the%20best%20universities%20in%20the%20country%20but%20is%20still%20grappling%20with%20a%20severe%20financial%20crisis.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20providing%20assistance%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20are%20engaging%20in%20a%20struggle%20to%20deteriorate%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20reputation.%20BJP%20is%20attempting%20to%20enter%20through%20the%20door%20left%20open%20by%20their%20representative%20to%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%E2%80%99s%20position.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20they%20created%20discord%20between%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20Governor%20in%20Kannur%2C%20Kerala%2C%20in%20a%20similar%20fashion.%20Our%20demand%20is%20for%20the%20punishment%20of%20the%20culprits%20%5Bin%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20suicide%5D%2C%20and%20to%20protect%20the%20campus%2C%E2%80%9D%20Biswas%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECritics%20of%20Hindutva%20ideology%20fear%20that%20like%20it%20did%20with%20JNU%2C%20the%20BJP%20plans%20to%20gain%20a%20foothold%20in%20JU%20by%20appointing%20those%20sympathetic%20to%20its%20ideology%20in%20high%20positions.%20These%20critics%20say%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20advocating%20for%20revisions%20that%20prioritise%20a%20specific%20historical%2C%20cultural%2C%20and%20religious%20perspective%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20movement%20aims%20to%20reshape%20the%20educational%20landscape%20in%20India%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20role%20of%20academia%20in%20nurturing%20a%20free-thinking%2C%20diverse%2C%20inclusive%2C%20and%20tolerant%20citizenry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Joydeep%20Sarkar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692623935000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FJadavpur_Wikimediafeatures.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjadavpur-university-new-vc-concerns-buddadeb-sau%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Due%20to%20Buddadeb%20Sau's%20association%20with%20unions%20that%20have%20links%20to%20the%20RSS-BJP%20and%20his%20past%20social%20media%20activity%2C%20concerns%20have%20been%20raised%20about%20the%20appointment.%20Others%20say%20he%20lacks%20the%20qualifications%20to%20satisfy%20the%20criteria%20laid%20out%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20is%20pouring%20nearly%20%24700%20million%20into%20internet%20access%20for%20rural%20communities%20so%20that%20kids%20don't%20'have%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20back%20of%20a%20mama's%20car%20in%20a%20McDonald's%20parking%20lot%20in%20order%20to%20do%20homework'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22832%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fiber%20optic%20cable%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58172cb4362ca41d008b5c76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22624%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReeltender%20Mo%20Laussie%20watches%20fiber-optic%20cable%20as%20he%20helps%20install%20the%20cable%20unto%20telephone%20poles%20June%2021%2C%202001%20in%20Louisville%2C%20CO.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Smith%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20announced%20nearly%20%24700%20million%20in%20funding%20for%20rural%2C%20high-speed%20internet%20projects.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20funding%20comes%20from%20the%20bipartisan%20infrastructure%20bill%2C%20which%20pours%20billions%20into%20internet%20access.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20round%20of%20funding%20will%20bolster%2037%20projects%20in%20rural%20areas%20across%2022%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20is%20following%20through%20on%20its%20aim%20to%20get%20rural%20areas%20connected%20to%20the%20Internet%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20time%2C%20they're%20putting%20nearly%20%24700%20million%20towards%20getting%2037%20projects%20across%2022%20states%20hooked%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20part%20of%20the%20latest%20tranche%20of%20funding%20from%20Biden's%20%241%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhats-in-the-infrastructure-bill-amtrak-clean-energy-2021-7%5C%22%3Etrillion%20bipartisan%20infrastructure%20law%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20allocated%20%2465%20billion%20towards%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-broadband-internet%5C%22%3Ehigh-speed%20broadband%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20money%20funds%2C%20in%20part%2C%20the%20USDA's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usda.gov%2Freconnect%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReConnect%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20disburses%20loans%20and%20grants%20to%20programs%20intended%20to%20get%20rural%20communities%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20too%20long%2C%20rural%20communities%20haven't%20had%20access%20to%20basic%20resources%20like%20affordable%2C%20reliable%2C%20high-speed%20internet%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitch%20Landrieu%2C%20senior%20advisor%20to%20the%20president%20and%20White%20House%20infrastructure%20coordinator%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20call.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20considering%20that%20we%20all%20know%20how%20essential%20internet%20is%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20it's%20beyond%20unacceptable%20that%20it's%20been%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%202018%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FCensus%2Flibrary%2Fpublications%2F2021%2Facs%2Facs-49.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECensus%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20internet%20use%2C%20Americans%20living%20in%20cities%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20internet%20access%20than%20their%20rural%20counterparts%3A%2086%25%20of%20urban%20households%20had%20an%20internet%20subscription%2C%20compared%20to%2081%25%20for%20rural%20households.%20White%20households%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20own%20a%20computer%20and%20have%20an%20internet%20subscription%20than%20Black%20households%2C%20and%20the%20more%20money%20a%20household%20makes%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20they%20were%20to%20own%20a%20computer%20or%20have%20an%20internet%20subscription.%20BroadBandNow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbroadbandnow.com%2Fresearch%2Ffcc-broadband-overreporting-by-state%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20estimated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20based%20on%20FCC%20data%2C%20that%20around%2042%20million%20Americans%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20broadband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Finternet%2F2021%2F09%2F01%2Fthe-internet-and-the-pandemic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20amidst%20work%20and%20school%20moving%20online%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20lower%20income%20internet%20users%20were%20more%20concerned%20about%20paying%20for%20their%20internet%20bills%20and%20more%20likely%20to%20experience%20internet%20connection%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration's%20connectivity%20push%20requires%20that%20programs%20receiving%20funding%20not%20only%20build%20out%20facilities%20that%20can%20provide%20high%20internet%20speeds%2C%20but%20also%20mandates%20that%20those%20projects%20apply%20to%20participate%20in%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fcc.gov%2Facp%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fcc.gov%2Facp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Einternet%20affordability%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20subsidize%20the%20cost%20for%20users.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20getting%20funding%20to%20communities%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20country%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20that%20no%20kid%20should%20have%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20back%20of%20a%20mama's%20car%20in%20a%20McDonald's%20parking%20lot%20in%20order%20to%20do%20homework%2C%26quot%3B%20Landrieu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20round%20of%20funding%20will%20help%20get%20thousands%20of%20residents%2C%20businesses%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20farms%20hooked%20up.%20You%20can%20check%20if%20your%20county%20or%20region%20is%20getting%20a%20new%20connection%20on%20the%20USDA's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rd.usda.gov%2Fmedia%2Ffile%2Fdownload%2Fusda-rd-reconnect-round4-tranche3-chart-08182023.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elist%20of%20grant%20awards%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Communities%20across%20Alaska%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20will%20receive%20nearly%20%24100%20million%20to%20have%20high-speed%20networks%20installed%3B%20those%20investments%20will%20impact%20nine%20educational%20facilities%20and%20nearly%202%2C200%20residents%2C%20per%20the%20USDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Internet's%20no%20longer%20a%20luxury%2C%20it's%20a%20necessity%20to%20fully%20participate%20in%20today's%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Landrieu%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20dealing%20with%20rural%20America%2C%20particularly%20high%20speed%20internet%20can%20connect%20people%20to%20economic%20and%20educational%20opportunities%20miles%20and%20even%20states%20away%2C%20close%20the%20rural%20health%20gap%20by%20increasing%20access%20to%20telemedicine%2C%20help%20farmers%20engage%20in%20precision%20agriculture%2C%20and%20so%2C%20so%20much%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfrastructure-biden-pouring-700-million-into-rural-high-speed-internet-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692623908000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dfccdfbd98a6001979aad1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfrastructure-biden-pouring-700-million-into-rural-high-speed-internet-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Residents%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20schools%20across%2022%20states%20will%20get%20access%20to%20high-speed%20internet%20under%20the%20new%20funding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfrastructure-biden-pouring-700-million-into-rural-high-speed-internet-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doors%20Shut%20For%20Ashwin%2C%20Chahal%20To%20Make%20India%20ODI%20Return%3F%20Rohit's%20Big%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20squad%20for%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20was%20announced%20on%20Monday%20and%20a%20big%20exclusion%20was%20veteran%20spinners%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20and%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal.%20Instead%2C%20the%20selectors%20went%20for%20the%20left-arm%20trio%20of%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20Kuldeep%20Yadav.%20During%20the%20press%20conference%20following%20the%20team%20selection%20meeting%2C%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20BCCI%20chief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20team%20selection%20and%20what%20it%20can%20mean%20for%20the%20future%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20ones%20who%20were%20not%20picked.%20%26quot%3BAxar%20Patel%20has%20done%20really%20well.%20He%20can%20bat%20too.%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20has%20had%20a%20fantastic%20run%20to%20this%20point.%20So%20someone%20had%20to%20miss%20out.%20Kuldeep%20is%20currently%20a%20little%20ahead%20of%20him%20(Chahal)%2C%20said%20Agarkar%20in%20the%20conference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20has%20had%20a%20fantastic%202023%20in%20white-ball%20cricket%2C%20taking%20seven%20wickets%20in%20three%20matches%20with%20the%20best%20figures%20of%204%2F6%20and%20eight%20wickets%20in%20seven%20T20Is%2C%20with%20the%20best%20figures%20of%203%2F28.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20Chahal%20has%20taken%20three%20wickets%20in%20two%20ODIs%20and%20nine%20wickets%20in%20nine%20T20Is.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkipper%20Rohit%20said%20that%20the%20team%20had%20a%20discussion%20about%20an%20off%20or%20leg%20spinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20also%20want%20someone%20who%20can%20bat%20at%20number%20eight%20and%20nine.%20Axar%20has%20had%20a%20great%20run%20with%20the%20bat%20in%20all%20formats%20and%20the%20IPL.%20He%20got%20some%20chances%20in%20West%20Indies%20too%2C%20but%20he%20bats%20too%20low.%20Him%20being%20there%20gives%20us%20batting%20depth%2C%20a%20left-hand%20option%20and%20someone%20who%20we%20can%20use%20up%20the%20order%20to%20play%20spin.%20We%20also%20thought%20of%20Ashwin%20(Ravichandran%20Ashwin)%20and%20Washi%20(Washington%20Sundar)%20as%20well.%20The%20only%20way%20we%20could%20include%20them%20was%20by%20having%20a%20seamer%20miss%20out.%20We%20cannot%20do%20this%20because%20seamers%20are%20going%20to%20be%20playing%20a%20massive%20role%20in%20the%20next%20two%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20door%20is%20open%20for%20all.%20If%20we%20need%20Chahal%20in%20World%20Cup%2C%20we%20will%20try%20to%20squeeze%20him%20in.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20Ashwin%20and%20Washington%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20open%20th