o%20be%20made%20in%20closed-end%20funds%2C%20which%20are%20ignored%20by%20Wall%20Street.%3Cp%3EReuters%20%2F%20Richard%20Brian%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBoaz%20Weinstein%2C%20Bill%20Ackman%2C%20and%20Marc%20Lasry%20have%20submitted%20a%20joint%20offer%20for%20Sculptor%20Capital%2C%20the%20WSJ%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20billionaire%20investors%20have%20made%20the%20bid%20at%20over%20%2412%20per%20share%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20it%20could%20get%20rejected%20-%20after%20Sculptor%20suggested%20the%20latest%20proposal%20it%20received%20has%20fallen%20short%20of%20expectations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBoaz%20Weinstein%2C%20Bill%20Ackman%20and%20Marc%20Lasry%20have%20joined%20forces%20to%20make%20an%20offer%20to%20buy%20New%20York-based%20alternative%20asset%20manager%20Sculptor%20Capital%20-%20but%20the%20bid%20could%20get%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20investors%20submitted%20their%20bid%20worth%20over%20%2412%20a%20share%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdeals%2Fwall-street-all-stars-including-weinstein-ackman-bid-for-hedge-fund-833726e0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20This%20is%20an%20improved%20offer%20from%20the%20trio%2C%20after%20an%20earlier%20one%20got%20spurned%2C%20the%20outlet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20renewed%20submission%20also%20appears%20to%20be%20at%20risk%20of%20getting%20rejected%20after%20Sculptor%20Capital%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20on%20Monday%2C%20without%20identifying%20the%20bidders%2C%20that%20a%20new%20proposal%20it%20received%20fell%20short%20of%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20received%20an%20unsolicited%20proposal%20from%20a%20third%20party%20that%20had%20participated%20in%20the%20strategic%20alternatives%20process.%20This%20bidder%20has%20not%20demonstrated%20adequate%20committed%20funding%20for%20any%20of%20its%20bids%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said%20in%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESculptor%20has%20already%20agreed%20to%20be%20taken%20over%20by%20another%20company%2C%20real-estate%20investment%20firm%20Rithm%20Capital%2C%20in%20a%20deal%20that%20values%20the%20struggling%20hedge%20fund%20at%20around%20%2411.15%20per%20share.%20On%20Friday%2C%20the%20shares%20closed%20at%20%2411.20%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20this%20latest%20bid's%20headline%20valuation%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20Rithm%20transaction%2C%20this%20proposal%20only%20includes%20committed%20financing%20for%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20amount%20required%20to%20consummate%20the%20transaction%20and%20underestimates%20the%20amount%20that%20would%20be%20necessary%20by%20several%20hundred%20million%20dollars%2C%26quot%3B%20Sculptor%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccordingly%2C%20in%20light%20of%20the%20foregoing%20and%20other%20issues%20with%20the%20proposal%2C%20the%20Special%20Committee%20has%20not%20determined%20that%20the%20bid%20is%2C%20or%20is%20reasonably%20expected%20to%20lead%20to%2C%20a%20Superior%20Proposal%20(as%20defined%20in%20the%20Company's%20merger%20agreement%20with%20Rithm)%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESculptor%20is%20the%20largest%20publicly-traded%20hedge%20fund%20with%20%2434%20billion%20of%20assets%20under%20management.%20It%20has%20faced%20controversy%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20stemming%20from%20the%20fallout%20from%20accusations%20of%20bribing%20government%20officials%20across%20several%20countries%20in%20Africa.%20In%202016%2C%20the%20firm%20had%20to%20pay%20%24412%20million%20in%20penalties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeinstein%20is%20most%20famous%20for%20profiting%20off%20the%20'London%20Whale'%20trading%20scandal%20that%20engulfed%20JPMorgan%20in%202012.%20Ackman%2C%20whose%20investment%20strategy%20is%20that%20of%20a%20shareholder%20activist%2C%20runs%20Pershing%20Squa