mpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bijuli%20Prasad%2C%20India's%20Oldest%20Elephant%2C%20Dies%20At%2089%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBijuli%20Prasad%2C%20the%20world's%20oldest%20Asiatic%20elephant%2C%20who%20lived%20royally%20in%20the%20tea%20gardens%20of%20Assam%20has%20died.%20The%20majestic%20jumbo%20age%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%2089%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBijuli%20Prasad%20breathed%20his%20last%20at%20the%20Behali%20tea%20estate%20of%20The%20Williamson%20Magor%20Group%20around%203.30%20am%20due%20to%20age-related%20issues%2C%20news%20agency%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPTI%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasad%20was%20named%20by%20his%20master%20Oliver%20Sahib%20from%20England.%20People%20who%20were%20associated%20with%20the%20jumbo%20including%20animal%20lovers%2C%20tea%20garden%20workers%C2%A0as%20well%20as%20locals%20gathered%20to%20mourn%20the%20death%20of%20the%20majestic%20jumbo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBijuli%20Prasad%20was%20a%20symbol%20of%20pride%20for%20The%20Williamson%20Magor%20Group.%20It%20was%20first%20brought%20to%20the%20Bargang%20tea%20estate%20as%20a%20calf%2C%20and%20later%20shifted%20here%20after%20the%20Bargang%20tea%20estate%20was%20sold%20off%20by%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20of%20the%20tea%20garden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPadma%20Shri%20awardee%20and%20famous%20elephant%20surgeon%20Dr%20Kushal%20Konwar%20Sarma%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20my%20knowledge%20is%20concerned%2C%20Bijuli%20Prasad%20was%20the%20oldest%20recorded%20domestic%20elephant%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%20Usually%2C%20the%20wild%20Asiatic%20elephants%20live%20up%20to%2062-65%20years%2C%20while%20the%20domestic%20ones%20survive%20till%20around%2080%20years%20with%20proper%20care%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20all%20its%20teeth%20fell%20off%20around%208-10%20years%20ago%2C%20Bijuli%20Prasad%20could%20not%20eat%20anything%20and%20was%20about%20to%20die.%20Then%20I%20went%20there%20and%20treated%20him.%20I%20had%20changed%20all%20his%20regular%20food%20and%20started%20mostly%20boiled%20food%20like%20rice%20and%20soybean%20with%20high%20protein%20value.%20This%20increased%20his%20longevity%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Sarma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692616680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fp4drpov8_indian-elephant-generic-istock_625x300_10_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbijuli-prasad-indias-oldest-elephant-dies-at-89-4315992%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bijuli%20Prasad%20breathed%20his%20last%20at%20the%20Behali%20tea%20estate%20of%20The%20Williamson%20Magor%20Group%20around%203.30%20am%20due%20to%20age-related%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbijuli-prasad-indias-oldest-elephant-dies-at-89-4315992%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbijuli-prasad-indias-oldest-elephant-dies-at-89-4315992%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbijuli-prasad-indias-oldest-elephant-dies-at-89-4315992%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hope%20is%20tested%20as%20search%20drags%20on%20for%20people%20missing%20in%20Maui%20fires%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692616475000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102908125%2Cimgsize-112590.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhope-is-tested-as-search-drags-on-for-people-missing-in-maui-fires%2Farticleshow%2F102907995.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102907995.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20wildfires%20that%20razed%20through%20historic%20Hawaiian%20town%20Lahaina%20have%20killed%20