s%20killed%20by%20the%20police%20team.%20The%20police%20called%20him%20a%20militant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20villagers%20countered%20the%20police%20version%20of%20the%20killing%2C%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Cstaged%E2%80%9D.%20Sengbath%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20thereafter%2C%20petitioned%20the%20Meghalaya%20high%20court%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20a%20fake%20encounter%20and%20demanding%20a%20probe%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheshillongtimes.com%2F2023%2F05%2F03%2Fhc-asks-cbi-to-investigate-oragitok-encounter-case%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EShillong%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20news%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20stated%20that%20as%20per%20the%20villagers%2C%20stones%20were%20thrown%20at%20Sengbath%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20leading%20him%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20Immediately%2C%20he%20was%20shot%20on%20the%20leg%20and%20then%20when%20he%20tried%20to%20flee%2C%20he%20was%20shot%20multiple%20times%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20death.%20After%20hearing%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20high%20court%20asked%20the%20CBI%20to%20take%20up%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F08%2F21%2Fdes65-cbi-encounter-case.html%5C%22%3EPTI%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20August%2020%20said%20the%20CBI%20has%20registered%20two%20cases%20on%20the%20matter%20based%20on%20two%20FIRs%20%E2%80%93%20one%20filed%20by%20state%20police%20and%20the%20other%20by%20the%20deceased%E2%80%99s%20father.%20The%20report%20quoting%20CBI%20officials%20said%20the%20special%20crime%20unit%20of%20the%20agency%20in%20Delhi%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20probe%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Meghalaya%20government%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fstory%2Fmeghalaya-becomes-ninth-state-to-withdraw-general-consent-to-cbi-324680-2022-03-03%5C%22%3Ewithdrawn%20the%20general%20consent%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20CBI%20for%20taking%20