20Seema%20to%20be%20deported%20to%20Pakistan.%20Both%20countries%20are%20occupied%20with%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1770453%23the-audacity-of-love%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Permalink%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20audacity%20of%20love%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardly%2076%20years%20ago%2C%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20were%20not%20separate%20countries.%20Today%2C%20when%20cumbersome%20restrictions%20prevent%20most%20Pakistanis%20from%20getting%20visas%20to%20visit%20India%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20the%20realisation%20of%20such%20romances%20are%20quite%20a%20feat.%20Last%20month%2C%20Anju%2C%20an%20Indian%20woman%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1766869%5C%22%3Ecrossed%20the%20border%20to%20marry%20Nasrullah%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20Pakistani%20man%20she%20met%20on%20Facebook.%20The%20audacity%20of%20love%20seems%20to%20have%20trumped%20the%20artifice%20of%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Seema%20and%20Sachin%E2%80%99s%20union%20shows%20not%20only%20that%20love%20can%20cross%20borders%2C%20but%20that%20borders%20inhibit%20love.%20Nationalist%20politics%20shape%20who%20can%20and%20cannot%20cross%20borders.%20While%20Seema%20may%20have%20a%20chance%20at%20staying%20in%20India%20with%20Sachin%2C%20not%20all%20lovers%20can%20cross%20the%20lines%20in%20the%20sand%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20colonial%20India-Pakistan%20border%20divides%20neighbours%20into%20citizens%20versus%20foreigners%2C%20natives%20versus%20migrants.%20The%20neighbouring%20countries%20with%20a%20shared%20past%20are%20building%20fences%2C%20separating%20kin%20and%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20these%20two%20lovers%20met%20virtually%20on%20an%20online%20gaming%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20that%20too%2C%20an%20online%20battleground%20%E2%80%94%20feels%20both%20farcical%20and%20uncannily%20apt.%20As%20nations%20increasingly%20fight%20their%20wars%20remotely%20and%20people%20divided%20by%20border%20walls%20meet%20on%20digital%20screens%2C%20life%20can%20feel%20like%20a%20simulation.%20Are%20Seema%20and%20Sachin%20disarming%20the%20nationalists%20and%20their%20hostilities%3F%20If%20nationals%20themselves%20are%20circumventing%20borders%20to%20realise%20their%20love%2C%20then%20who%20are%20these%20nations%20for%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Seema%20and%20Sachin%E2%80%99s%20union%20is%20a%20victory%20for%20lovers%2C%20it%20is%20also%20fodder%20for%20haters.%20Their%20union%20yokes%20Pakistan%20and%20India%2C%20as%20mother%20and%20mother-in-law.%20Crossing%20the%20threshold%20between%20the%20figurative%20daughter%20and%20daughter-in-law%2C%20Seema%20is%20both%20reviled%20and%20welcomed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20social%20media%2C%20Indians%20are%20calling%20Seema%20a%20Pakistani%20spy.%20For%20Pakistanis%2C%20she%20is%20an%20Indian%20spy%2C%20allegedly%20evinced%20by%20her%20being%20a%20Sindhi%20and%20converting%20to%20Hinduism.%20Can%20Sachin%2C%20a%20Hindu%20man%2C%20satisfy%20Seema%3F%20Will%20a%20woman%20who%20converts%20be%20able%20to%20return%20to%20her%20family%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajoritarian%20Pakistani%20Muslims%20bemoan%20the%20loss%20of%20one%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctheir%E2%80%9D%20women%2C%20while%20majoritarian%20Indian%20Hindus%20question%20the%20loyalties%20of%20%E2%80%9Canother%E2%80%99s%E2%80%9D%20woman.%20A%20woman%20in%20love%20threatens%20both%20Indians%20and%20Pakistanis.%20As%20nationalists%20across%20borders%20invoke%20the%20same%20xenophobic%20tropes%2C%20in%20different%20idioms%2C%20the%20colourful%20flags%20of%20respective%20nations%20seem%20to%20blur%20into%20each%20other%2C%20leaving%20us%20with%20a%20familiar%20story%20of%20men%20trying%20to%20regulate%20women%E2%80%99s%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1770453%23the-patron-states-of-women%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Permalink%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20patron%20states%20of%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Partition%2C%20both%20countries%20have%20made%20themselves%20patriarchal%20patrons%20of%20women.%20Seema%20has%20petitioned%20to%20stay%20in%20India%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20it%20is%20her%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fpakistani-citizen-seema-haider-files-mercy-petition-with-president-droupadi-murmu-news-304980%3Futm_source%3Drelated_story%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematrimonial%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Post-independence%2C%20both%20governments%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcore.ac.uk%2Fdownload%2Fpdf%2F229475513.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagreed%20to%20recover%20and%20exchange%20abducted%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0following%20Partition%20in%201947.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20announced%20itself%20as%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fgeeta-indias-daughter-wont-be-sent-back-to-pakistan-sushma-swaraj%2Farticleshow%2F66713966.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efoster%20parent%20of%20Geeta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20woman%20who%20lived%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20Indian%20state%20making%20an%20exception%20for%20a%20Pakistani%20Muslim%20woman%20to%20stay%2C%20so%20far%2C%20in%20the%20country%20is%20touching%20and%20troubling%20in%20this%20moment%20of%20nationalist%20rule.%20In%20a%20patriarchal%2C%20Hindu%20nationalist%20India%2C%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20imagine%20the%20converse%2C%20where%20a%20Pakistani%20Muslim%20man%20falling%20in%20love%20with%20an%20Indian%20Hindu%20woman%20would%20be%20welcomed.%20Neither%20would%20an%20Indian%20Hindu%20groom%20likely%20be%20welcomed%20in%20Pakistan.%20As%20a%20scholar%20of%20migration%20across%20these%20countries%E2%80%99%20borders%2C%20I%20recognise%20how%20states%20selectively%20welcome%20people%20based%20on%20their%20religion%2C%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20gender%2C%20sexuality%2C%20and%20nationality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20some%20constricting%20veins%20of%20South%20Asian%20popular%20culture%20celebrate%20the%20inter-religious%20unions%20of%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20%E2%80%94%20think%20Jodhaa%20and%20Akbar%2C%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20and%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20%E2%80%94%20a%20popular%20welcoming%20of%20inter-caste%20and%20queer%20unions%20are%20unfortunately%20beyond%20the%20national%20and%20international%20pale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENationalist%20politics%20unequally%20determine%20who%20can%20cross%20human-made%20walls%2C%20yielding%20a%20wide%20gap%20in%20%E2%80%9Ctravel%20freedom%E2%80%9D.%20Only%20when%20we%20stop%20questioning%20the%20movements%20of%20individuals%20and%20start%20questioning%20the%20legality%20of%20national%20borders%20that%20impinge%20on%20our%20rights%20to%20migrate%2C%20will%20we%20see%20a%20true%20challenge%20to%20nationalist%20politics%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20we%20need%20to%20pay%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20who%20gets%20to%20cross%20borders%20and%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20Here%20is%20to%20more%20lovers%2C%20in%20all%20directions%2C%20being%20united.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENatasha%20Raheja%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20researcher.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1770453%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20Dawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692612911000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21145542%2Falexandre-debieve-h081KBDNdIo-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fone-woman-in-love-threatens-both-indians-and-pakistanis%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20Sachin-Seema%20saga%2C%20majoritarian%20Pakistani%20Muslims%20bemoan%20the%20loss%20of%20one%20of%20%E