f-kerala-suspension-rss%5C%22%3Esuspension%20of%20Gilbert%20Sebastian%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20issue.%20He%20was%20penalised%20for%20teaching%20a%20class%20on%20fascism.%20Neither%20have%20we%20heard%20any%20action%20from%20the%20teaching%20community%20of%20the%20institute%20of%20Kolhapur%2C%20which%20sent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1052201%2Frevoke-kolhapur-professors-forced-leave-who-said-rapists-could-be-from-any-religion-say-academics%5C%22%3ENiranjana%20Desai%20on%20leave%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20telling%20her%20students%20that%20rapists%20could%20be%20from%20any%20community.%20We%20have%20also%20not%20heard%20about%20any%20protest%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fpune%2Fsymbiosis-professor-held-pune-objectionable-remarks-hindu-deities-8875111%2F%5C%22%3Efaculty%20member%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Symbiosis%20College%20of%20Arts%20and%20Commerce%20who%20was%20arrested%20and%20suspended%20for%20a%20talk%20he%20gave%20in%20his%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20numerous%20violations%20of%20academic%20freedom%20in%20universities%20and%20colleges%20across%20India%2C%20but%20no%20such%20strikes%20were%20organised%20by%20the%20teaching%20community%2C%20despite%20their%20history%20of%20protesting%20against%20various%20service-related%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20and%20teachers%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fgallery%2F2016%2F2%2F18%2Fnew-delhi-protest-thousands-call-for-students-freedom%5C%22%3Eprotested%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202016%20after%20its%20students%20were%20attacked%20during%20a%20protest.%20But%20after%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20how%20academics%20watched%20anxiously%20while%20their%20colleagues%20were%20being%20attacked%2C%20penalised%2C%20and%20even%20jailed%20to%20defend%20their%20right%20to%20academic%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fjnu-sedition-case-chargesheet-kanhaiya-kumar-umar-khalid-5537648%2F%5C%22%3EJNU%20incident%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20treated%20more%20as%20a%20political%20reaction%20to%20a%20political%20attack%20even%20when%20we%20know%20that%20it%20was%20essentially%20a%20matter%20of%20academic%20freedom.%20Students%20like%20Kanhaiya%20Kumar%2C%20Umar%20Khalid%2C%20Anirban%20Bhattacharya%2C%20Rama%20Naga%20and%20others%20were%20attacked%20for%20having%20organised%20a%20meeting%20at%20the%20campus%20on%20the%20subject%20of%20Kashmir.%20However%2C%20beyond%20its%20strong%20and%20vocal%20protest%2C%20we%20have%20not%20seen%20the%20teaching%20community%20convey%20to%20the%20authorities%20that%20teaching%20is%20meaningless%20if%20academic%20freedom%20is%20compromised.%20So%2C%20if%20a%20teacher%20is%20persecuted%20for%20his%20research%2C%20teaching%20cannot%20go%20on%20as%20usual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20step%20that%20makes%20the%20protest%20by%20Ashoka%20University%E2%80%99s%20academic%20community%20extraordinary.%20It%20centres%20the%20question%20of%20academic%20freedom%20in%20a%20way%20not%20done%20before.%20Ashoka%20University%E2%80%99s%20academic%20community%20needs%20to%20be%20supported%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fashoka-university-sabyasachi-das-pulapre-balakrishnan%5C%22%3Espirited%20defence%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Sabyasachi%20Das.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fashoka-is-falling-short-of-its-declared-vision-300-academics-express-solidarity-with-sabyasachi-das%5C%22%3EAshoka%20Is%20Falling%20Short%20of%20Its%20Declared%20Vision%E2%80%99%3A%20300%2B%20Academics%20Express%20Solidarity%20With%20Sabyasachi%20Das%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20case%20of%20Ashoka%20University%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20all%20the%20centres%20and%20departments%20of%20the%20university%20have%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Das%2C%20who%20was%20forced%20to%20resign%20after%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fashoka-university-facultys-research-paper-on-bjp-manipulation-in-2019-election-triggers-row%5C%22%3Eresearch%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20possible%20manipulation%20of%20the%20election%20process%20in%20the%202019%20general%20elections%20was%20attacked%20by%20the%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20Students%20and%20teachers%20have%20questioned%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20management%2C%20asking%20it%20to%20reinstate%20Das.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20research%20paper%20argued%20that%20there%20was%20a%20possibility%20that%20the%20election%20process%20was%20manipulated%20in%20closely%20contested%20seats%20to%20benefit%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20research%20paper%20created%20excitement%20within%20academic%20circles%2C%20its%20sampling%2C%20methodology%2C%20and%20findings%20were%20under%20examination.%20But%20the%20BJP%20members%20took%20offence%20and%20unleashed%20an%20online%20attack%20on%20Das.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20us%20have%20faced%20such%20an%20attack%20for%20writing%20an%20article%20or%20making%20a%20speech.%20However%2C%20in%20most%20of%20the%20cases%2C%20the%20university%20administration%20did%20not%20think%20it%20necessary%20to%20intervene.%20But%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Das%2C%20the%20members%20of%20the%20governing%20board%20intervened%2C%20forcing%20the%20administration%20to%20institute%20an%20enquiry%20to%20look%20into%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20research%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20extraordinary%20step%20by%20the%20university%20administration%20to%20have%20even%20thought%20about%20such%20a%20step.%20Looking%20into%20the%20quality%20of%20a%20research%20paper%20and%20whether%20it%20is%20academically%20sound%20or%20not%20is%20not%20the%20job%20of%20the%20administration.%20This%20is%20best%20done%20by%20peers.%20But%20here%2C%20the%20governing%20board%20thought%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20was%20entering%20an%20area%20which%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20in%20its%20purview.%20It%20was%20attempting%20to%20dictate%20to%20the%20teachers%20how%20research%20should%20be%20conducted.%20We%20learnt%20that%20there%20were%20well-intentioned%20suggestions%20made%20to%20Das%20to%20change%20the%20title%20of%20the%20paper%20to%20make%20it%20sound%20more%20neutral%20and%20ask%20him%20to%20refrain%20from%20talking%20about%20it%20till%20the%20enquiry%20was%20over.%20He%20was%20free%20to%20teach%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20was%20absurd%20and%20made%20no%20sense.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20administration%20was%20effectively%20telling%20the%20academic%20community%20to%20not%20trust%20Das.%20What%20was%20to%20be%20investigated%20in%20the%20paper%3F%20Das%20had%20already%20invited%20the%20academic%20community%20for%20comments%20and%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20the%20governing%20board%20interfered%20with%20academic%20work%20which%20was%20outside%20its%20domain.%20Is%20there%20any%20guarantee%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20restrict%20the%20university%20from%20inviting%20people%20who%20are%20disliked%20by%20the%20current%20regime%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshoka%20University%E2%80%99s%20governing%20board%20has%20shown%20that%20it%20succumbs%20to%20pressure%20from%20the%20regime.%20It%20chose%20to%20part%20ways%20with%20a%20celebrated%20scholar%20like%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Mehta%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Famid-ashoka-university-row-a-look-at-professors-who-quit-their-posts-in-protest-8896760%2F%5C%22%3Ewho%20had%20consistently%20questioned%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20ruling%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20that%20there%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F990333%2Fdismantling-the-labyrinth-what-i-learnt-about-power-and-privilege-when-i-quit-ashoka-in-2016%5C%22%3Ewere%20dismissals%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20faculty%20member%20and%20another%20employee%20for%20their%20being%20part%20of%20a%20petition%20on%20Kashmir.%20On%20both%20these%20occasions%20there%20were%20murmurs%20of%20protest%20but%20no%20decisive%20step%20taken%20by%20the%20university%20community%20to%20defend%20its%20space%20which%20is%20academic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsafeguarding-academic-freedom-is-the-bedrock-of-indias-constitutional-morality%5C%22%3ESafeguarding%20Academic%20Freedom%20Is%20the%20Bedrock%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Constitutional%20Morality%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnother%20line%20of%20argument%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20academic%20community%20at%20Ashoka%20University%20can%20only%20direct%20its%20protests%20towards%20the%20governing%20board.%20There%20is%20an%20ongoing%20debate%20in%20the%20public%20sphere%20regarding%20the%20wisdom%20of%20targeting%20these%20board%20members.%20The%20argument%20put%20forth%20is%20as%20follows%3A%20It%20was%20only%20due%20to%20pressure%20from%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20that%20the%20board%20was%20compelled%20to%20take%20action.%20They%20are%20acting%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20safeguarding%20the%20university%2C%20and%20they%20believe%20that%20a%20small%20sacrifice%20can%20be%20made%20for%20greater%20objectives.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20not%20to%20cast%20blame%20on%20the%20governing%20board%2C%20as%20we%20must%20acknowledge%20that%20they%20had%20good%20intentions%20when%20they%20established%20this%20university%2C%20with%20the%20betterment%20of%20liberal%20education%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccountability%20should%20be%20placed%2C%20the%20argument%20goes%20on%2C%20at%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20doorstep%20for%20coercing%20the%20administration%20into%20taking%20this%20unwelcome%20step.%20The%20governing%20board%20has%20numerous%20responsibilities%20to%20sustain%20the%20university%2C%20unlike%20Das%2C%20who%20appears%20to%20be%20primarily%20concerned%20with%20his%20academic%20integrity.%20These%20board%20members%20are%20taking%20on%20a%20difficult%20task%20for%20a%20higher%20purpose%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20accept%20being%20seen%20as%20compromised%20individuals.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20remember%20that%20they%20have%20been%20pressured%20into%20taking%20this%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20argument%20sounds%20persuasive%20and%20is%20also%20true%20to%20a%20great%20extent.%20Das%20was%20not%20served%20with%20a%20notice%20proactively%20by%20the%20board.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20have%20any%20problem%20with%20the%20paper.%20But%20it%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20disregard%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20ruling%20regime%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20university.%20Keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20interest%20of%20hundreds%20of%20students%2C%20scores%20of%20faculty%20members%20and%20the%20image%20of%20the%20university%2C%20it%20had%20to%20take%20the%20unwelcome%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20should%20we%20accept%20this%20line%20of%20argument%3F%20Remember%20how%20Rutgers%20University%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftwitter-faceoff-rutgers-university-backs-controversial-historian-audrey-truschke-netizens-react%2Farticleshow%2F81412939.cms%5C%22%3Ebacked%3C%2Fa%3E%20Audrey%20Truschke%20when%20she%20was%20attacked%20on%20social%20media%20by%20some%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20groups%E2%80%99%20for%20her%20so-called%20%E2%80%9CHinduphobic%20statements%E2%80%9D%3F%20The%20university%20could%20have%20easily%20distanced%20itself%20from%20her.%20However%2C%20it%20did%20not.%20That%20is%20how%20the%20administrators%20of%20a%20university%20are%20expected%20to%20behave.%20They%20have%20to%20defend%20their%20faculty%20and%20students%20from%20external%20pressure%20and%20attack%20and%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshoka%20University%E2%80%99s%20community%20must%20demand%20answers%20from%20its%20board.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20the%20fight%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a