ns%2C%20and%20give%20voice%20to%20the%20issues%20of%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21122023%2FIMG_3083.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21122023%2FIMG_3083.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21122023%2FIMG_3083-300x183.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21122023%2FIMG_3083-1024x625.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668935%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22733%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAnnie%20Raja%20gives%20a%20speech%20as%20the%20Delhi%20police%20blockades%20the%20We20%20summit.%20Photo%3A%20John%20Dayal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThomas%20Franco%20from%20People%20First%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CArticle%2019%20(1)%20of%20the%20constitution%20provides%20for%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20freedom%20of%20expression.%20No%20law%20prevents%20people%20from%20gathering%20for%20a%20peaceful%20discussion.%20We%20condemn%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20take%20away%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%20Shaktiman%20Ghosh%20of%20the%20National%20Hawkers%E2%80%99%20Federation%20condemned%20the%20police%20action%20and%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20will%20fight%20against%20these%20fascist%20trends%2C%20come%20what%20may.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20police%20at%20the%20gates%2C%20the%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20building%20was%20one%20of%20a%20community%20cultural%20gathering.%20The%20ground%20floor%20saw%20stalls%20of%20political%20and%20economic%20literature%2C%20the%20works%20of%20Ambedkar%2C%20stalls%20of%20Khadi%20clothes%2C%20handbags%20and%20paintings%2C%20and%20on-the-spot%20work%20by%20young%20artists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20organisers%2C%20who%20had%20the%20permission%20of%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20premises%20to%20hold%20the%20event%2C%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Finching-closer-to-a-police-state-we20-summit-organisers-after-police-refuses-permission-on-day-3%5C%22%3Eserved%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20notice%20denying%20them%20permission.%20They%20then%20decided%20to%20cut%20short%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20third%20day.%20The%20many%20delegates%20staying%20in%20the%20building%20left%20for%20home%20on%20August%2020%2C%20but%20not%20before%20passing%20the%20We20%20Declaration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20failures%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20the%20G20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20sessions%20on%20the%20first%20two%20days%2C%20economists%2C%20political%20scientists%20and%20civil%20society%20leaders%20called%20the%20bluff%20of%20the%20Modi%20administration%20which%20was%20projecting%20to%20the%20leaders%20of%20G20%20nations%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20was%20%E2%80%9Cgoverning%20India%20in%20the%20best%20traditions%20of%20liberal%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20inaugural%20programme%20on%20August%2018%20had%20a%20panel%20of%20speakers%20including%20Brinda%20Karat%2C%20Manoj%20Jha%2C%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20Arun%20Kumar%2C%20Hannan%20Mollah%2C%20Teesta%20Setalvad%2C%20Medha%20Patkar%2C%20Jayati%20Ghosh%2C%20Rajeev%20Gowda%2C%20Franco%20Thomas%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20six%20workshops%20on%20day%202%20focussed%20on%20global%20finance%2C%20big%20banks%2C%20and%20their%20impact%20on%20people%3B%20the%20right%20to%20information%3B%20digital%20data%20and%20surveillance%3B%20and%20climate%20change.%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20Vandana%20Shiva%2C%20Anjali%20Bhardwaj%2C%20Amrita%20Johri%20and%20Nikhil%20Dey%20were%20among%20the%20speakers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20failure%20on%20several%20fronts%2C%20including%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20civil%20liberties%2C%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20people%20along%20the%20coastline%2C%20the%20exploitation%20of%20gig%20workers%20in%20the%20digital%20and%20app-based%20marketplaces%2C%20and%20assaults%20on%20freedom%20of%20religion%20and%20belief%20came%20up%20for%20detailed%20analysis.%20A%20young%20woman%20living%20and%20farming%20on%20the%20Yamuna%20riverbed%2C%20having%20been%20displaced%20multiple%20times%2C%20spoke%20of%20the%20human%20cost%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%20as%20hutment%20dwellers%20have%20lost%20their%20homes%20to%20bulldozers%20which%20are%20%E2%80%9Cbeautifying%20the%20capital%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%20every%20speaker%20questioned%20the%20massive%20public%20spending%20on%20the%20G20%20preparations%2C%20with%20tens%20of%20crores%20spent%20on%20advertising%20alone%2C%20which%20centred%20on%20Modi%20alone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20economist%20Jayati%20Ghosh%20pointed%20out%2C%20the%20G20%20summit%20remains%20an%20informal%20elite%20club%2C%20holding%20all%20its%20discussions%20behind%20closed%20doors%2C%20with%20no%20participation%20from%20the%20people%20who%20are%20affected%20by%20their%20decisions%20and%20recommendations.%20It%20is%20going%20to%20be%20less%20about%20the%20real%20concerns%20of%20the%20people%20and%20more%20of%20a%20prescription%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmasters%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21122039%2FIMG_3085.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22