20discuss%20the%20ongoing%20turmoil%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20could%20not%20take%20place%20today%20due%20to%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20get%20a%20nod%20from%20the%20governor%20Anusuiya%20Uikey.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20it%2C%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20which%20has%20also%20been%20demanding%20that%20the%20governor%20call%20a%20session%20of%20the%20assembly%20along%20with%20several%20other%20national%20parties%20to%20discuss%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20conflict%2C%20said%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20governor%20to%20summon%20the%20session%20%E2%80%9Ccan%20lead%20to%20a%20constitutional%20crisis%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20border%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20ago%2C%20on%20August%2020%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Okram%20Ibobi%20Singh%2C%20speaking%20at%20the%20party%20office%20in%20Imphal%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20looks%20like%20the%20demand%20(for%20the%20session)%20has%20fallen%20on%20deaf%20ears%20and%20chances%20of%20the%20much-awaited%20assembly%20sitting%20seem%20slim%20at%20this%20point.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIbobi%20Singh%20called%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98Monsoon%20Session%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20assembly%2C%20and%20therefore%20implied%20that%20this%20was%20a%20scheduled%20session%20which%20should%20have%20taken%20place%20after%20the%20March%20session.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20governor%20is%20supposed%20to%20call%20the%20summon%2015%20days%20before%20the%20actual%20sitting%20since%20the%20state%20assembly%20prorogue%20had%20already%20been%20conducted%20but%20no%20such%20actions%20have%20been%20meted%20out%20from%20the%20governor%20till%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fdelay-leading-to-crisis-ibobi%5C%22%3Ean%20%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said%20quoting%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20news%20report%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20this%20crucial%20juncture%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20people%2C%20it%20is%20better%20to%20avoid%20such%20potential%20constitutional%20breakdown.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20cabinet%E2%80%99s%20recommendation%20having%20failed%20to%20secure%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20approval%2C%20the%20question%20arises%20under%20what%20circumstances%20the%20governor%20may%20not%20comply%20with%20such%20a%20recommendation%20from%20the%20cabinet%20headed%20by%20the%20chief%20minister.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202016%2C%20in%20the%20judgment%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3ENabam%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ERebia%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%2C%20a%20constitutional%20bench%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fnews-analysis-governor-cannot-employ-his-discretion-and-should-strictly-abide-by-the-aid-and-advice-of-the-cabinet-to-summon-house-supreme-court%2Farticle32191699.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520five-judge%2520Constitution%2520Bench%2520judgment%2520of%2520the%2520Supreme%2Cadvice%25E2%2580%259D%2520of%2520the%2520Cabinet%2520to%2520summon%2520the%2520House.%5C%22%3Ethe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20when%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20House%2C%20the%20governor%20is%20to%20summon%20the%20House%20with%20the%20aid%20and%20advice%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20cabinet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESignificantly%2C%20in%20the%2060-member%20house%2C%20while%2010%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20had%20refused%20to%20attend%20the%20session%20citing%20their%20safety%20in%20Imphal%2C%2010%20others%20from%20the%20Naga%20community%20were%20also%20asked%20by%20the%20apex%20body%20of%20the%20Nagas%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20United%20Naga%20Council%20(UNC)%2C%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-naga-mlas-biren-singh-kuki-separate-administration%5C%22%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%208%20Naga%20MLAs%20Back%20CM%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Move%20Against%20Kukis%E2%80%99%20Separate%20Administration%20Demand%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%2040%20other%20legislators%20from%20the%20valley%2C%20a%20sizeable%20lot%20are%20from%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rebel%20camp%20which%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20leadership%20change%20prior%20to%20the%20May%203%20violence.%20Those%20rebel%20MLAs%20were%20not%20signatory%20to%20a%20recent%20memorandum%20submitted%20to%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20by%2040%20MLAs%20from%20the%20state%20urging%20him%20to%20maintain%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20Manipur.%20Among%20the%2040%20MLAs%20were%20eight%20Naga%20MLAs%20from%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20allies%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Naga%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20and%20Nationalist%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2027%2C%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20had%20announced%20that%20the%20cabinet%20had%20recommended%20an%20assembly%20session%20and%20the%20request%20had%20been%20forwarded%20to%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20office.%20State%20information%20and%20public%20relations%20minister%20Sapam%20Ranjan%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20issued%20to%20local%20press%20that%20the%20cabinet%20had%20asked%20for%20the%20session%20to%20be%20held%20on%20the%20third%20week%20of%20August.%20On%20August%204%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmanipur-cabinet-recommends-governor-to-summon-assembly-session-on-aug-21%2F623906.html%5C%22%3E%20the%20state%20government%20formally%20asked%20the%20governor%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20convene%20the%20session%20on%20August%2021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20former%20BJP%20ally%2C%20the%20Kuki%20People%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%20(KPA)%2C%20refused%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20session%20(it%20has%20two%20MLAs)%20accusing%20the%20state%20government%20of%20organising%20it%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20powerful%20civil%20society%20body%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20the%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%2C%20the%20UNC%20too%20cited%20the%20same%20reason%20for%20asking%20MLAS%20from%20the%20Naga%20community%20to%20avoid%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20late%20July%2C%20COCOMI%20had%20been%20seeking%20a%20special%20session%20of%20the%20assembly%20and%20had%20adopted%20August%205%20as%20the%20deadline%20for%20it%20to%20the%20state%20government%20at%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Imphal%20on%20July%2029.%20COCOMI%20had%20been%20seeking%20a%20resolution%20in%20the%20assembly%20to%20maintain%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20the%20state%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Kuki%20MLAs%20demanding%20a%20separate%20state%20or%20a%20Union%20Territory%20for%20the%20community.%20On%20August%207%2C%20a%20delegation%20of%20COCOMI%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20at%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%2C%20seeking%20a%20special%20session.%20COCOMI%20spokesperson%20Kh.%20Athouba%20had%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20then%20that%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20session%20had%20been%20raised%20by%20them%20because%20they%20had%20not%20%E2%80%9Cseen%20any%20initiative%20from%20the%20legislators%20or%20the%20state%20government%20to%20discuss%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20assembly%20is%20not%20dissolved%2C%20so%20it%20must%20assemble%20to%20deliberate%20on%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20discussing%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20from%20a%20set%20of%20MLAs.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%2010%20MLAs%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community%20have%20stated%20their%20indiv