%99%20to%20resign%20from%20Ashoka%20University%20after%20a%20paper%20he%20authored%2C%20on%20possible%20manipulation%20in%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20drew%20the%20ire%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20their%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshoka%20University%20has%20been%20criticised%20for%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20as%20the%20varsity%20had%20publicly%20distanced%20itself%20from%20Das%E2%80%99s%20paper%20after%20the%20political%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20academics%E2%80%99%20full%20statement%20and%20list%20of%20signatories%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20the%20undersigned%20members%20of%20the%20academic%20fraternity%2C%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20forced%20%E2%80%98resignation%E2%80%99%20of%20Sabyasachi%20Das%2C%20Assistant%20Professor%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Economics%2C%20Ashoka%20University.%20Das%E2%80%99s%20paper%20%E2%80%98Democratic%20Backsliding%20in%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Largest%20Democracy%E2%80%99%20which%20analysed%20the%20probability%20of%20electoral%20manipulation%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202019%20elections%20came%20under%20significant%20flak%20from%20the%20party.%20The%20University%20issued%20a%20statement%20dissociating%20itself%20from%20the%20research.%20Following%20this%2C%20from%20what%20has%20emerged%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20the%20Governing%20Body%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%98evaluate%E2%80%99%20the%20%E2%80%98merit%E2%80%99%20of%20his%20paper.%20Dr%20Das%20subsequently%20resigned.%20It%20is%20clear%20from%20this%20sequence%20of%20events%20that%20what%20was%20at%20stake%20was%20not%20the%20academic%20merit%20of%20his%20paper%2C%20but%20the%20threat%20it%20posed%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20detailed%20academic%20counter%20to%20this%20paper%2C%20only%20ad%20hominem%20attacks%20in%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Pulapre%20Balakrishnan%20of%20the%20Economics%20department%20subsequently%20resigned%20from%20Ashoka%20University%20in%20solidarity%2C%20student%20organisations%20have%20issued%20strong%20statements%20in%20support%20of%20Dr%20Das%2C%20the%20Economics%20department%2C%20followed%20by%20several%20other%20departments%20have%20also%20strongly%20criticized%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20actions%2C%20and%20asked%20for%20the%20reinstatement%20of%20Dr%20Das%2C%20failing%20which%20they%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20carry%20on%20their%20teaching%20obligations.%20Over%2080%20faculty%20members%20have%20signed%20a%20separate%20statement%20asking%20for%20a%20charter%20on%20academic%20freedom%20created%20in%202021%20to%20be%20implemented%2C%20including%20a%20committee%20on%20academic%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20backsliding%20on%20Dr%20Das%E2%80%99s%20academic%20freedom%20because%20the%20topic%20he%20chose%20to%20study%20was%20inconvenient%20to%20one%20political%20party%2C%20the%20university%20violates%20several%20principles%20of%20academic%20freedom.%20This%20episode%20also%20shows%20that%20private%20universities%20do%20not%2C%20despite%20all%20their%20claims%20to%20the%20contrary%2C%20serve%20as%20bulwarks%20of%20liberal%20thought.%20The%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20the%20government%20is%20applying%20equal%20pressure%20on%20both%20private%20and%20public%20universities%20%2Finstitutions.%20Ashoka%2C%20by%20caving%20in%20to%20the%20pressure%20is%20falling%20short%20of%20its%20own%20declared%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20welcome%20the%20strong%20resistance%20by%20members%20of%20Ashoka%20University%E2%80%99s%20student%20body%2C%20faculty%20and%20alumni%20and%20joins%20them%20in%20asking%20for%20the%20immediate%20reinstatement%20of%20Dr%20Das%20and%20concrete%20steps%20to%20ensure%20academic%20freedom%20in%20Ashoka%20University.%20We%20hope%20that%20the%20Ashoka%20University%20imbroglio%20shall%20form%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20wide%20ranging%20discussion%2C%20encompassing%20both%20private%20and%20public%20institutions%2C%20about%20the%20necessity%20of%20a%20charter%20that